title: 'Making the Leap' debate
itunes:title: 'Making the Leap' debate
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- react to the latest NFL news including Jason Pierre-Paul's firework incident (7:53) and Odell Beckham's latest gripe (14:12). The guys then review the latest "Making the Leap" candidates (21:57) before trying to find a new outro song for the show (43:25).
